  <brief_title>Letrozole Versus Laparoscopic Ovarian Drilling in Polycystic Ovary Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Letrozole Versus Laparoscopic Ovarian Drilling for Clomiphene-resistant Women With Polycystic Ovary Syndrome</official_title>
